title: Windows 7 Ultimate Sp1 X64 April 2018 Team-LiL
description:
Windows 7 Ultimate Sp1 X64 April 2018 Team-LiL

made by lil-fella (Team-LiL)

when the windows Seven loads up for the first time SAD3 drivers installer will load and start unpacking drivers. then after unpacking the drivers the install process will take place. if there is a D folder in the c drive you may delete the D folder once all drivers have installed.

there is a extras folders on the root of the disk which can be used if you need Windows.7.loader

ive NOT set this disk to pre activate as some people might not want this. so your given the choice to use your own key if you have one



use Rufus to make USB installation media from iso image


please visit team-lil webpage for more info and pics
